## 📌 Tasks Completed

### ✅ Task 1: Basic Network Sniffer
- Developed a Python-based network sniffer using Scapy
- Captured live network packets
- Extracted:
  - Source IP address
  - Destination IP address
  - Protocol type (TCP/UDP)
- Helped understand how data flows in a network

---

